#. module: energy_selfconsumption
#: model:mail.template,body_html:energy_selfconsumption.selfconsumption_insciption_form
msgid ""
"<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\n"
"                    <p>Hello <t t-out=\"ctx.get('partner_name')\"></t>.</p>\n"
"                    <p>\n"
"                        Thank you very much for your interest in participating in the shared self-consumption project of the Energy Community <t t-out=\"object.name\"></t>.\n"
"                        We have successfully received your registration request and we will keep you informed of the next steps to be taken.\n"
"                    </p>\n"
"                    <p>\n"
"                        If you have any questions, please do not hesitate to contact us.\n"
"                    </p>\n"
"                    <p>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"object.name\"></t>\n"
"                    </p>\n"
"                </div>\n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"            \n"
"        <p>Hola ${ ctx['partner_name'] }.</p>\n"
"        <p>\n"
"            Muchas gracias por tu interés en participar del proyecto de autoconsumo compartido de la Comunidad Energética ${ object.name }.\n"
"            Hemos recibido correctamente tu solicitud de inscripción y ya te iremos informando de los siguientes pasos que se vayan dando.\n"
"        </p>\n"
"        <p>\n"
"            Para cualquier duda, seguimos en contacto.\n"
"        </p>\n"
"        <p>\n"
"            ${ object.name }\n"
"        </p>\n"
"            \n"
"        "

#. module: energy_selfconsumption
#: model:mail.template,body_html:energy_selfconsumption.selfconsumption_energy_delivered_invoicing_reminder
msgid ""
"<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\n"
"                    <p>Hi,</p>\n"
"                    <p>\n"
"                        Remember that the collective self-consumption project\n"
"                        <b><t t-out=\"object.name\"></t></b>\n"
"                        of the energy community\n"
"                        <b><t t-out=\"object.project_id.company_id.comercial_name or object.project_id.company_id.name\"></t></b>\n"
"                        must invoice on the day <b><t t-out=\"ctx.get('next_invoicing')\"></t></b>.\n"
"                    </p>\n"
"                    <p>\n"
"                        It is necessary, therefore, that you enter into Odoo the energy generated in kWh during the period\n"
"                        <b><t t-out=\"ctx.get('first_date')\"></t></b>\n"
"                        - <b><t t-out=\"ctx.get('last_date')\"></t></b>.\n"
"                    </p>\n"
"                    <p>\n"
"                        To do so, go to the project file, enter the contracts view, select the contracts that must be invoiced and\n"
"                        press the Invoice button.\n"
"                    </p>\n"
"                    <p>\n"
"                        For any questions or incidents, contact the support team; support@somcomunitats.coop.\n"
"                    </p>\n"
"                </div>\n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"            \n"
"        <p>Hola,</p>\n"
"        <p>\n"
"            Recuerda que el proyecto de autoconsumo colectivo\n"
"            <b>${ object.name }</b>\n"
"            de la comunidad energética\n"
"            <b>${ object.project_id.company_id.name }</b>\n"
"            debe facturar el día <b>${ ctx['next_invoicing'] }</b>.\n"
"        </p>\n"
"        <p>\n"
"            Es necesario, por lo tanto, que ingreses en Odoo la energía generada en kWh durante el periodo\n"
"            <b>${ ctx['first_date'] }</b>\n"
"            - <b>${ ctx['last_date'] }</b>.\n"
"        </p>\n"
"        <p>\n"
"            Para hacerlo vaya a la ficha del proyecto, ingrese a la vista de contratos, seleccione los contratos que se deben facturar y\n"
"presione el botón Facturar.</br>\n"
"        </p>\n"
"        <p>\n"
"            Para cualquier duda o incidencia contacta con el equipo de soporte; soporte@somcomunitats.coop.\n"
"        </p>\n"
"            \n"
"        "

#. module: energy_selfconsumption
#: model:mail.template,body_html:energy_selfconsumption.selfconsumption_energy_delivered_custom_invoicing_reminder
msgid ""
"<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\n"
"                    <p>Hi,</p>\n"
"                    <p>\n"
"                        Remember that the collective self-consumption project\n"
"                        <b><t t-out=\"object.name\"></t></b>\n"
"                        of the energy community\n"
"                        <b><t t-out=\"object.project_id.company_id.comercial_name or object.project_id.company_id.name\"></t></b>\n"
"                        must invoice on the day <b><t t-out=\"ctx.get('next_invoicing')\"></t></b>.\n"
"                    </p>\n"
"                    <p>\n"
"                        It is necessary, therefore, that you upload to the Som Comunitats platform\n"
"                        the energy delivered from each CUPS for this period. Instructions to\n"
"                        generate invoices:.\n"
"                    </p>\n"
"                    <p>\n"
"                        1. Go to the project file, go to the contracts view and select the\n"
"                        contracts to be invoiced.\n"
"                    </p>\n"
"                    <p>\n"
"                        2. In the Action button, select the \"Generate invoices\" option.\n"
"                    </p>\n"
"                    <p>\n"
"                        3. In the wizard, load the CSV file with the energy delivered in kWh during\n"
"                        the period <t t-out=\"ctx.get('first_date')\"></t> - <t t-out=\"ctx.get('last_date')\"></t> for each CUPS and\n"
"                        press the \"Generate\" button.\n"
"                    </p>\n"
"                    <p>\n"
"                        4. Finally, you must validate and send the generated invoices. If you have\n"
"                        any doubts or issues, please contact our support team:\n"
"                        soporte@somcomunitats.coop\n"
"                    </p>\n"
"                </div>\n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"            \n"
"        <p>Hi,</p>\n"
"        <p>\n"
"            Remember that the collective self-consumption project\n"
"            <b>${ object.name }</b>\n"
" of the energy community\n"
"            <b>${ object.project_id.company_id.name }</b>\n"
" must invoice on the day <b>${ ctx['next_invoicing'] }</b>.\n"
"        </p>\n"
"        <p>\n"
"            It is necessary, therefore, that you upload to the Som Comunitats platform\n"
" the energy delivered from each CUPS for this period. Instructions to\n"
" generate invoices:.\n"
"        </p>\n"
"        <p>\n"
" 1. Go to the project file, go to the contracts view and select the\n"
" contracts to be invoiced.\n"
"        </p>\n"
"        <p>\n"
" 2. In the Action button, select the \"Generate invoices\" option.\n"
"        </p>\n"
"        <p><strong>Generar facturas</strong 3. En el asistente, cargue el fichero CSV con la energía suministrada en kWh durante\n"
" el periodo ${ ctx['primera_fecha'] } - ${ ctx['last_date'] } para cada CUPS y \n"
"pulsar el botón \"Generar\".\n"
"        </p> <p        <p 4. Por último, debe validar y enviar las facturas generadas. Si tiene\n"
" cualquier duda o incidencia, ponte en contacto con nuestro equipo de soporte:\n"
" soporte@somcomunitats.coop\n"
"        </p>\n"
"            \n"
"        "

#. module: energy_selfconsumption
#: model:mail.template,body_html:energy_selfconsumption.selfconsumption_power_acquired_invoicing_reminder
msgid ""
"<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\n"
"                    <p>Hi,</p>\n"
"                    <p>\n"
"                        The collective self-consumption project\n"
"                        <b><t t-out=\"object.name\"></t></b>\n"
"                        of the energy community\n"
"                        <b><t t-out=\"object.project_id.company_id.comercial_name or object.project_id.company_id.name\"></t></b>\n"
"                        has started the invoicing process on <b><t t-out=\"ctx.get('next_invoicing')\"></t></b> according to the established recurrence.\n"
"                    </p>\n"
"                    <p>\n"
"                        Invoices are created in \"draft\" and it is therefore necessary that they be validated and sent as soon as possible.\n"
"                    </p>\n"
"                    <p>\n"
"                        For any questions or incidents, contact the support team; support@somcomunitats.coop.\n"
"                    </p>\n"
"                </div>\n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"<p>Hola,</p>\n"
"        <p>\n"
"            El proyecto de autoconsumo colectivo\n"
"            <b>${ object.name }</b>\n"
"            de la comunidad energética\n"
"            <b>${ object.project_id.company_id.name }</b>\n"
"            ha iniciado el proceso de facturación el día <b>${ ctx['next_invoicing'] }</b> según la periodicidad establecida.\n"
"        </p>\n"
"        <p>\n"
"            Las facturas se crean en “borrador” y por tanto es necesario que sean validadas y enviadas lo antes posible.\n"
"        </p>\n"
"        <p>\n"
"            Para cualquier duda o incidencia contacta con el equipo de soporte; soporte@somcomunitats.coop.\n"
"        </p>"

